<div align='center'>
  <h2>Welcome to BioPartsBuilder</h2>
</div>
<hr />

<div align='center'>
  <%= form_tag({:action => "search_result"}, :method => "post", :multipart => true) do %>
    <%= text_field_tag :sequence, '', :class => 'genome_search' %>
    <br />
    Query Example: organism:Saccharomyces cerevisiae AND feature:CDS &nbsp; &nbsp; 
    <a href="#myModal" data-toggle="modal">see full syntax instruction</a>
    <br /><br />
    <%= submit_tag("Search Designed Part", :class => "btn btn-primary") %>
  <% end %>
</div>
<div class='container'>
  <hr />
  <p>Please cite us: <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/26568632" target='_blank'>Yang K, Stracquadanio G, Luo J, Boeke JD, Bader JS. <b>BioPartsBuilder: a synthetic biology tool for combinatorial assembly of biological parts.</b> <i>Bioinformatics</i>. 2015 Nov 14. pii: btv664.</a></p>
</div>
<br /><br />

<div id="myModal" class="modal hide fade" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-header">
    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">Ã—</button>
    <h3 id="myModalLabel">Syntax Guide</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-body">
    <p>You can input any words to search all the fields, or search a specific field using the format: field_name:words. 'AND', 'OR' can be used to combine diffrent fields to create complex queries.</p>
    <b>Keywords</b>
    <table class='table table-striped table-bordered'>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Keyword</th>
          <th>Description</th>
          <th>Query Example</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>name</td>
          <td>Part name</td>
          <td>name:*cob*</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>accession_number</td>
          <td>Sequence accession number</td>
          <td>accession_number:YAL*</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>organism</td>
          <td>Oganism latin name</td>
          <td>organism:Saccharomyces cerevisiae</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>feature</td>
          <td>Entity type, e.g. CDS, tRNA, promoter</td>
          <td>feature:CDS</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>sequence</td>
          <td>Part sequence</td>
          <td>sequence:*vqhimageppsmvadtl*</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</div>

